{"tid":1442035,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罪案率低　香港膺全球最安全旅遊城市勝星洲","createTime":"2019-08-10T20:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T04:20:15.000Z","uid":58841,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"693b1a2a0283fc2072030f5071c4e9ba7279ccc8","tid":1442035,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:35:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://美國調查機構Backgroundchecks.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8BBackgroundchecks.org&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU1I2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=d6c2393d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">美國調查機構Backgroundchecks.org</a>公布最新全球最安全旅遊城市/國家排名，亞洲地區囊括首三位，香港排名第一，新加坡及日本跟緊其後。調查機構指香港的罪案率持續下降，加上不如新加坡有一個專制的政府，亦沒有如日本的自然災害，是全球旅客的安全旅遊目的地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Bep8et.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Bep8et.png&h=30f0a6f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbztQsP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbztQsP.jpg&h=360fa820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n調查機構根據罪案率、國家保安、自然災害等項目評定各地表現，對旅客而言，香港被評為全球最安全的目的地，因香港有建全的法律、政府及文化，不論男女，都可以無憂地在白天或晚上外出，不用擔心人身安全。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.nnews.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/frc-478327cb5b3d4bb4ae5d7e3b06d1a1d7.jpg?ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.nnews.eu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Ffrc-478327cb5b3d4bb4ae5d7e3b06d1a1d7.jpg%3Fssl%3D1&h=7bdc2a95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，調查機構指香港天氣潮濕、屬亞熱帶氣候、人口密度高，以及鄰近中國廣東省，或令香港較易爆發傳染病，一如2003年發生沙士疫情，可幸此類爆發只屬偶有及少數，未有動搖香港在安全城市的排名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZYuzUp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZYuzUp.jpg&h=1946a66a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e7c10efd6e1542ec9692dfdfe62c00ff0f9d38e","tid":1442035,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:36:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6741ee37fe663d92bbc054fe08edf3be828991f9","tid":1442035,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:41:51.000Z","msg":"世界十大最安全的城市，中国香港被誉为&ldquo;亚洲最安全城市&rdquo;之一！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.auliving.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/15653292851-640x358.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.auliving.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F15653292851-640x358.png&h=54812cc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港是我们中国最为安全的城市，但是相信大家和小编一样对于香港的印象全部都是来自于电影电视剧，那个拿着刀两个不同阵地的两伙人拿着刀、斧头，蓄势待发的一场乱斗即将开始，这也是香港早些年的现象，如今的香港已经成为了&ldquo;亚洲最安全的城市&rdquo;之一，香港是一个犯罪率非常低的城市，警察比例高，警察通宵巡视街道，这也大大的降低了犯罪率。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/c31f16_43b9ff6c5b18499db474b0d01b32eaf4~mv2_d_4178_2739_s_4_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fc31f16_43b9ff6c5b18499db474b0d01b32eaf4~mv2_d_4178_2739_s_4_2.jpg&h=121c3511&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd9eb72f089cb809811c4258b7e474b5eaf15136","tid":1442035,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d63e688a0a15695436cc8c94d34a3fb98ff2122","tid":1442035,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T20:56:26.000Z","msg":"本港屬全球罪案率最低城市之一 張建宗：警隊功不可沒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2918779/org/06ad7a650387f5dfdc6dc2f984ecbc83.jpg/cAINnm5PMLRdScCIGKsBGRpiP7LMU4PNOx_mfjsf5n4?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2918779%2Forg%2F06ad7a650387f5dfdc6dc2f984ecbc83.jpg%2FcAINnm5PMLRdScCIGKsBGRpiP7LMU4PNOx_mfjsf5n4%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=bd97035c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年是香港警隊成立175周年，政務司司長張建宗今於網誌提及本港屬全球罪案率最低的城市之一，去年首11個月總體罪案更按年跌2.9%，讚揚香港警隊於維持治安及社會秩序方面的優越表現有目共睹，警隊擔當重要的執法者角色，功不可沒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrKdFDN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrKdFDN.gif&h=d28e436f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他於網誌表示，2017年香港整體罪案是42年來新低，單是去年港首11個月總體罪案有50122宗，較2017年同期更下跌2.9%；而「世界正義工程」(World Justice Project) 發表《2017-18全球法治指數》，香港在秩序與治安位列全球第4，令港人引以為傲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1aHU1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1aHU1h.jpg&h=e9e26cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張建宗直言，香港良好法治管治及安全城市的美譽得來不易，是建基於高效的執法水平；除警務處，其他紀律部隊同事，亦在不同崗位服務市民，締造安居樂業的好環境，讓人深感驕傲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/police-01_FB5P8_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpolice-01_FB5P8_1200x0.png&h=31541aab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a26821c26ccba8ff2888326de4f1b381adc6b58","tid":1442035,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:02:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f87184829422c4e4120ed0ab794dbc1acba2333","tid":1442035,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ffdf375e9ae044d6186b575c0c893bd18991b1","tid":1442035,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f810cdad0ec09b1f9b695e089ab8bcd4295e99ed","tid":1442035,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T21:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8e5ae7658cb073321c5ec91d2ef97065623f50","tid":1442035,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣